Pakistan were fined 1 over for a slow over rate

milestones.description: Carl Hooper and Chanderpaul's 154-run partnership is WI's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 152 between Clive Lloyd and Viv Richards

stories.title: Hooper ton salvages face-saving victory for Windies
stories.summary: Skipper Carl Hooper's masterful unbeaten 112 helped the West Indies put a daunting 260 on the board, and the Caribbean attack put enough pressure on Pakistan to rustle up a win by a whopping 110 runs
